        <p><i>To present notions of Financial Mathematics, Financial Management and Economic Engineering to students, enabling them to build and analyze cash flows from projects and enterprises, discuss the main aspects of financial management in industrial, commercial and service companies and analyze and propose strategies for financial management related to market and production strategies.</i></p>
        
